text: Margaret Kate Weedon was an archer from Great Britain. She was born on 31 October 1853 and died on 19 October 1930. Weedon competed at the 1908 Summer Olympics.Margaret WeedonMargaret WEEDON == References == Category:1853 births Category:1930 deaths Category:British archers Category:Olympians for Great Britain
